snippet.title: HeyUGuys
snippet.description:
Welcome the one and only HeyUGuys.com YouTube channel or Hey You Guys if you want to be grammatically correct :)

Here you'll find our interviews with the world's biggest movie stars conducted at red carpet premieres, press conferences and one to one interview settings that we like to call junkets.

We cover all things film from the smallest independent productions to the biggest Hollywood blockbusters.
